metadata.name: #1 | Fourteen
metadata.description:
- The first 1/1 NFT in the collection
- Extremely high quality

The first pain happened to me when I was 14: I was sexually raped.

On that day, an innocent, virginal, unaware-of-life fourteen-year-old girl felt the cruelty, rudeness, anger, and aggression.

What will happen to her in the future and how will her life change? Only God knew.

In the picture you can see me, experiencing such pain for the first time. There is paint on my back and thighs which everyone can perceive differently.
